headline: Cummins Unveils B7.2 Diesel Engine for Medium-duty Applications
summary: COLUMBUS, Ind., March 05, 2025--Today global power and technology leader Cummins Inc. (NYSE: CMI) announced an update to the legendary B-Series engine platform, unveiling the new Cummins B7.2 diesel engine at NTEA Work Truck Week in Indianapolis, IN.
